name: Agog 2 Luminous Scribble
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D scribble sculpture. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
